{"id": "1429736476450623579", "channel_id": "1429736476450623579", "type": 0, "author_id": "134873210490585089", "author_name": "jearbear", "author_bot": false, "content": "After the patch the button to buy cores with silver from the gacha page is gone. It wasn't in the patch notes but if it could come back that would be nice.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T07:42:19.205000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1429736476660203583", "filename": "ohowp7lx17wf1.webp", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 8352, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1429736476450623579/1429736476660203583/ohowp7lx17wf1.webp?ex=69ff8e1b&is=69fe3c9b&hm=b531cc2c399cf229420604bc262bc6be6c4d04adbe6ef994a43f4e78d046f980&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429736476450623579", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Purchase cores from awaken menu?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1429894425160581270", "channel_id": "1429894425160581270", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi BIAV,\n\nSome of the older players and I were talking about the new design choices and are a little sad with the direction.\n\nWe like it when a unit comes out and it has mechanics that can add/interact with other units/realm mechanics. Corposant was a great new unit. She added to the aftershock group of units. Similarly, recently adding aftershock to Cassiah's kit is great!\n\nHowever, a lot of the other recent new units feel like they are in a vacuum with their kits. They add this new layer specific only to them. Most are not interacting with previous mechanics like, sacrifice, counter, poison.....and the game feels like it's missing mechanic interactions to discover.\n\nThis brings me to Pollux. His kit feels like he plays really well with Castor, but it doesn't seem (maybe I haven't discovered it yet) a way to make his finishing card move  \"Cleaning Judgement\" stronger by using a completely different unit.\n\nExample: Corposant added to Aurita being able to do more damage. These interactions are what I love to find and build around.\n\nPollux just seems like, tank and wait style (very blue). Play heart, play castor plume -> then eventually play Cleaning Judgement. But I haven't found a way to increase Cleansing Judgement DMG with already in game mechanics with another unit (*maybe its too early*). This loss of interactions to buff your unit's finisher move is just sad to me.\n\nA suggestion is to have his Cleansing Judgement add a mechanic -> increase dmg by X for every other card (not just his own) played before this card this turn. -> Now there is a mechanic I am looking for ways to optimize. This is fun to me. Rather than the basic play card, build up layers, do damage.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T18:09:57.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 20}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429894425160581270", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Pollux and Game Feedback", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1429789180808007800", "channel_id": "1429789180808007800", "type": 0, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "因为这次卡斯托尔的复刻写的是特别复刻活动好像和常规的复刻有区别，那这次特别复刻会不会占用其原本的复刻周期呢？", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T11:11:44.903000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429789180808007800", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "这次卡斯托尔的复刻会占用原本的复刻周期吗？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1361169005435420785"]}
